<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.2">
<l>tuḷampaṭu muṟuval tōḻiyark karuḷāḷ tuṇaimulai cāntukoṇ ṭaṇiyāḷ</l>
<l>kuḷampaṭu kuvaḷaik kaṇṇiṇai yeḻutāḷ kōlanaṉ malarkkuḻaṟ kaṇiyāḷ</l>
<l>vaḷampaṭu munnīr vaiyamuṉ ṉaḷanta māleṉṉum māliṉa moḻiyā</l>
<l>ḷiḷampaṭi yivaḷuk keṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She does not grace her friends with [smiling] teeth like pomegranate [seeds];</l>
<l rend="indent"> she does not adorn her paired breasts with sandal paste.</l>
<l>She does not line her two eyes [which are like] lotuses rising from a pond;</l>
<l rend="indent">she does not adorn her curls with fine, beautiful flowers.</l>
<l>She is one whose words [have] a type of madness which say,</l>
<l rend="indent">“O Māl who once measured the fertile, ocean [-encircled] earth!”</l>
<l>What were you intending for [this] maiden, lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
